# Common File Methods

| Method         | Purpose                                        |
| -------------- | ---------------------------------------------- |
| `open()`       | Opens a file                                   |
| `close()`      | Closes a file                                  |
| `read()`       | Reads entire file or specified characters      |
| `readline()`   | Reads one line                                 |
| `readlines()`  | Reads all lines into a list                    |
| `write()`      | Writes text to a file                          |
| `writelines()` | Writes multiple lines                          |
| `seek()`       | Moves file pointer                             |
| `tell()`       | Returns current file pointer position          |
| `flush()`      | Forces buffered data to be written to the file |
